author: The Linux Foundation
description:
The Open Source Congress report outlines a vision for:
🔹 Collaboration that goes beyond annual events
🔹 A unified response to regulatory and cybersecurity challenges
🔹 Partnerships that sustain and grow the ecosystem
Let’s build a secure, collaborative future together.
📖 Dive into the details:  https://www.linuxfoundation.org/research/2024-open-source-congress
title: What’s next for open source?
